init_text: A woman has been dating guy after guy, but it never seems to work out. She's unaware that she's actually been dating the same guy over and over; a shapeshifter who's fallen for her, and is certain he's going to get it right this time.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: "You're getting much better at this," he said, giving himself a smile.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: It was full of hipsters; the kind that dressed up in thrift-store clothes and called themselves 'retro'.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: Her hair was long and black, but the blue of her top brought out some reddish highlights.
